Revision history for Perl extension OpenGL::Simple.

0.01  Sat Dec 28 00:19:36 2002
	- original version; created by h2xs 1.21 with options
		-A -a -n OpenGL::Simple

0.02  Sat Aug 28 15:07:00 BST 2004
        - merged patches from Max Maischein and Autrijus Tang to fix
          Makefile.PL on win32 and FreeBSD respectively.
        - added gluLookAt

0.03  Thu Nov 10 13:19:51 GMT 2005
        - Added a bunch more calls, although the evaluator and pixel
          calls still need finishing off.
        - Some small fixes to build on MacOS.
